abstract: >
  A public roof inspection documentation standard and machine-readable
  protocol package for residential roof inspection evidence capture, slope
  mapping, photo sequencing, hail and wind condition documentation, roof damage
  label taxonomy, Claim Verifiability, and AI-readable roof condition reporting.
keywords:
  - roof inspection
  - roof inspection documentation
  - Inspector Roofing Protocols
  - hail damage
  - wind damage
  - storm damage documentation
  - Claim Verifiability
  - JSON Schema
  - OpenAPI
  - AI-readable roofing documentation
